==English==

===Etymology===
Some claim an acronym for [[good|Good]] [[old|Old]] [[raisins|Raisins]] and [[peanuts|Peanuts]], but this is probably a [[backronym]].  The Oxford English Dictionary cites a 1913 reference to the verb "gorp", meaning "to eat greedily".

